{
  "stem": "2097.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But now, if I think back, I know that there was a plan, they way they did it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because there was nobody left, and no man left in the town-- only the children and the older ones.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1942.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Christians, they were drafted to the army, to the regular army-- but not as the Jew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Jew was taken-- everyone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't even realize what that-- that-- the way happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They drafted by each month, a certain age or a certain group-- by addresses, by the street.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know how they did it, exactly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that the way it happen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in 1942, I was 13 years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So my mother had a lot of harsh time-- a hard time, because she didn't know what to work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She didn't know what to do, how to keep the children, the home-- because the-- we had-- we had two tenants.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And because we were Jews and they were Christians, they didn't have to pay-- only 1/2 a amount of the rent, which wasn't enough, for the-- even, for the tax.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Two tenants we had in the house-- my-- my parents' house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And since they didn't had-- they didn't have to pay the full amount of the rent, my mother had very hard time to keep the house, and to feed the two children.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So finally, she learned how to sew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was doing alterations and new shirts for a store.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she kept that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She fed us.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
